Content: I have a 125 ttr 2008 which I can’t get started. It was running fine 3 years ago but took it out of the garage to get it running again a few weeks ago and can’t get it started. So far I have done the following: 1) replaced the gas with new gas 2) replaced the carburetor 3) changed the spark plug It still won’t start. It turns over just fine but won’t start. Any recs on what to do next?
